## What I built

A Flask + SQLite wiki with everything requested:

- **Read access for anyone** — page index (`/`), individual pages (`/wiki/<title>`), and title search (`/search`).
- **Editing for logged-in users only** — `/new` and `/wiki/<title>/edit` are gated by a `@login_required` decorator; register/login/logout with hashed passwords (Werkzeug).
